The paper proposes a new model for learning molecular representations using graph-structured data. The model is based on attention mechanisms and global dependencies, which are common in natural language processing and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
